---
title: Cal Smart Middle East-Inspired Turkey Patties with Mint Tabbouleh and Lemon Aioli
description: Fresh and herbaceous, tabbouleh is a staple in Lebanese fare! Typically paired with parsley, we've made this version with mint. Together with spiced turkey patties and a lemon aioli, this dish is patio-ready!
